A simple Document Management System (eFile) that allows
District, Municipal and Regional assemblies to keep records
of Inward and Outward correspondences.

The application also features an chat /  messaging system for 
Officers to communicate and share files between themselves in an
organisation.

Future Developments:
1. Fee fixing integration
2. Statistics on total entries of correspondences in the system using chats
3. Show number of users (active) online.
4. Display Polls and Rss feeds into the site
5. Chat bot for user interaction and advance search.